keholders to get the job done.\nI would welcome to work with James again if I had the opportunity.", "recommendations/0/name": "James Young", "recommendations/0/subtitle": "Hospitality Operator & Leader 9 countries | Europe, Middle East, SE Asia & Australasia | IHG & WMC Group | Multi-unit operations & sustainable growth | Award-winning hotels & teams in Vietnam | MBA with Distinction | FIH", "recommendations/0/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/jamesyounglxvii/", "recommendations/0/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAABwc2IBp_PXsnfIWFt8iskhzmnNiQRuW5s", "recommendations/1/context": "Pascal worked with Michel on the same team", "recommendations/1/date": "April 11, 2020", "recommendations/1/description": "Michel is a charismatic leader who has lived and worked in many different countries and continents. I know Michel as a very knowledgeable person who has a humble personality.\nHis ability to interact with many different stakeholders on varies levels, proves that he has a dynamic and adaptable personality. \nMichel is someone who gets the job done whilst motivating the team to explore new avenues if needed. His ability to understand the needs of different owners and translate them into a strategic and tactical approach is something to admire.  ", "recommendations/1/name": "Michel Chertouh", "recommendations/1/subtitle": "Luxury Hospitality Leader | Managing Director at Regent Hong Kong", "recommendations/1/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/michel-chertouh-901408/", "recommendations/1/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAAPaxEBeTzLsemqRqlP39NS20t3LOw1TdM", "recommendations/2/context": "Pascal was Bella's client", "recommendations/2/date": "January 27, 2019", "recommendations/2/description": "Thao is a dedicated sales person. She is motivated and knows the details about the products she is offering. \nThao is a high energy person and her perseverance to ensure her clients are satisfied is very high. ", "recommendations/2/name": "Bella Thao Nguyen", "recommendations/2/subtitle": "Community Operation Specialist at TDCX", "recommendations/2/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/bella-thao-nguyen-945682a2/", "recommendations/2/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAABXQAsUBFhJ-xpi5VTL1YRkb_-o-R5d_GwE", "recommendations/3/context": "Pascal managed Tara directly", "recommendations/3/date": "September 27, 2018", "recommendations/3/description": "Tara reported to me while working at the InterContinental Saigon. Tara's perseverance and drive for results are her outstanding competencies to achieve success. She also has a good eye for detail and doesn't shy away to coach the team about her touch. \n\nTara's ability to create a family atmosphere and get things accomplished at the same time is invaluable. By engaging her team and motivating them, she is keeping everyone on their toes to achieve targets within deadlines. Her all round approach to revenue, expenses as well as colleagues and guests satisfaction completes the picture to a well rounded overall adaptable leadership style.", "recommendations/3/name": "Tara Nguyen", "recommendations/3/subtitle": "20yr Global Hotel People Leader - IHG, Four Seasons, and Rosewood - Leadership roles in both US and Asia", "recommendations/3/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/taranguyen/", "recommendations/3/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAABHvAv0BJeNZmhvTYfnD1YQUGGcW6UprEXk", "recommendations/4/context": "Pascal was senior to Bao but didn't manage Bao directly", "recommendations/4/date": "September 21, 2018", "recommendations/4/description": "I had the pleasure of working with Bao for my tenure at the InterContinental Saigon. Bao was the Director of Finance and Business Support and oversaw all financial aspect of the hotel and residences and worked closely with the owners for the financial statement and procedures.\nBao is not someone who only looks at expenses and tries to squeeze for more profit. He is someone who also approaches the business from a revenue point of view. He is someone who will challenge the revenue committee how the hotel can achieve better revenues and he is not afraid of challenging the status quo.\n\nBao has a very thorough financial background and is able to deal with the different stakeholders as well as different operation teams with ease. His commitment to supporting the business and drive for results and excellence is high.", "recommendations/4/name": "Bao Nguyen", "recommendations/4/subtitle": "Resort Manager | Finance & Business Support at InterContinental Phu Quoc Long Beach Resort", "recommendations/4/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/bao-nguyen-7064698/", "recommendations/4/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAF91rYBF6BXMEwf0686APLSk-xrCoQXBW0", "recommendations/5/context": "Pascal was senior to Walaa but didn't manage Walaa directly", "recommendations/5/date": "September 8, 2014", "recommendations/5/description": "During my time in Cairo I worked with Walaa at the InterContinental Citystars.\nWalaa is someone who works hard and won't go home before she knows that everything for the events are taken care of, either internally or from the guest's point of view. \nHer ability to interact with guests and other departments give her the edge to get things done well and in a timely manner.\n\nIt was a pleasure to work with her and wouldn't hesitate to hire her back in my team.", "recommendations/5/name": "Walaa Emam", "recommendations/5/subtitle": "Director of Catering and Conferences Services The Nile Ritz Carlton", "recommendations/5/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/walaa-emam-26b5386b/", "recommendations/5/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAA7Z1nMBnexAqKABEa0Uy5OiXukGpLm7XBg", "recommendations/6/context": "Pascal worked with Ken on the same team", "recommendations/6/date": "February 3, 2014", "recommendations/6/description": "I was appointed the organizer on behalf of InterContinental Citystars Cairo for IHG's EMEA leadership's conference in November 2010. Ken was organizing the conference on behalf of IHG.\n\nIt was a real pleasure working with Ken on the preparation and execution of this important event. Ken's experience in organizing events, his creativity to turn problems into managable challenges and his detailed follow up set us up for success.\nNothing was too much for Ken to handle; He relayed questions swiftly and ensured a timely follow up to complete certain issues and move on to the next.\nDuring the conference Ken was always on the floor checking on current events while keeping a close eye on the preparations for the next stage.\n\nThe positive feedback after the event was overwhelming and a credit to Ken.", "recommendations/6/name": "Ken Pahkim", "recommendations/6/subtitle": "Event Producer and Strategic Events Manager. Service design experience, event and production management", "recommendations/6/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/kenpahkim/", "recommendations/6/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAABGlAEBZ7Yx63Qs9uk1SYzHvhcJQdlv_aI", "recommendations/7/context": "Pascal managed Antonio directly", "recommendations/7/date": "November 27, 2012", "recommendations/7/description": "It was a pleasure working with Tony for the 18 months we worked together in Saigon.\nTony has a wealth of experience in the day to day operations of the Engineering Department. He doesn't shy away of an issue and always looks for the root cause to permanently resolve the problem.\n\nTony took the lead in our Fire Life Safety programs and ensured 100% compliance to brand standards. At the same time he is thinking and planning ahead.\n\nOur environmental programs have been set up with Tony's leadership and our energy consumption has reduced year over year.\n\nTony is a very qualified Director of Engineering and I wouldn't hesitate in recommending him or re-hiring him.", "recommendations/7/name": "Antonio Dizon, PME,CEOE,CEM", "recommendations/7/subtitle": "Director Of Engineering at Shangri-La The Fort Manila", "recommendations/7/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/antonio-dizon-pme-ceoe-cem-5b50258/", "recommendations/7/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAFtRxkBTs5zFmZiY9PLCKDky4Li3WLS9d0", "recommendations/8/context": "Pascal was senior to Hazem but didn't manage Hazem directly", "recommendations/8/date": "May 6, 2012", "recommendations/8/description": "Hazem is detail oriented and keeps his strategic goals in mind when taking care of the day to day business in the reservations department.\n\nHe was a good leader and took time to develop his team. He made sure the team was aligned and were supporting eachother.\n\nHazem has a great career ahead of him and I wish him success.", "recommendations/8/name": "Hazem Shawki , MBA, DBA", "recommendations/8/subtitle": "Commercial Leader | Strategist | Total Revenue Optimization | Lateral thinking | Marketing & Sales | Emotional Intelligence | Digital transformation ​| Change Management | Operations & Finance Support | Unlocking Teams", "recommendations/8/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/hazem-shawki-mba-dba-0120a212/", "recommendations/8/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAKBF44BoSyaWfCxqS9OIDdD13mmV_UBkio", "recommendations/9/context": "Pascal worked with Chaitanya on the same team", "recommendations/9/date": "January 27, 2012", "recommendations/9/description": "Chaitanya is a detailed oriented person while not losing sight of the big picture and goals. He looks into different streams of revenue opportunities and digs into the different channels details with the team to maximize revenues.\nThe ways of working of Chaitanya with the different members of the team was motivating and accomodating.\n\nIt was a pleasure working with Chaitanya.", "recommendations/9/name": "Chaitanya Rane", "recommendations/9/subtitle": "Commercial Director | Multi-Property Portfolio Leadership | Revenue · Pricing · Distribution | Hotels & Tourism | EMEA & APAC | 17 yrs | Hilton", "recommendations/9/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/chaitanyarane/", "recommendations/9/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAJ_Bk0BgDp6T3urIZTzjRes1d8S5SutlL8", "recommendations/10/context": "Pascal was senior to Jim but didn't manage Jim directly", "recommendations/10/date": "September 5, 2011", "recommendations/10/description": "I enjoyed working with Jim. Our property was old and Jim would never go for the 'quick fix'. He would always ensure things were fixed properly. He is innovative in finding alternative ways if the traditional solution doesn't work.\nWhatever you ask Jim, he will assist and bring it to a close. He goes beyond the call of his regular duties.", "recommendations/10/name": "Jim Stone", "recommendations/10/subtitle": "Director Of Engineering at Shutters on the Beach", "recommendations/10/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/jim-stone-3582541a/", "recommendations/10/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAPzqfQBChLSfXkdcMBGdlSH7G5AACWYRGQ", "recommendations/11/context": "Pascal was senior to CATHERINE ANN but didn't manage CATHERINE ANN directly", "recommendations/11/date": "July 26, 2011", "recommendations/11/description": "Working with Cathy at Citystars was pleasant. She was always smiling and had the ability to take care of guests in an extreme service minded way. Her eye to detail, anticipation of guests' needs and organization were some of her strong points.\nI would employ Cathy again if the opportunity came up.", "recommendations/11/name": "CATHERINE ANN D. RUTAQUIO", "recommendations/11/subtitle": "Regional Food Service Manager", "recommendations/11/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/catherine-ann-d-rutaquio-a326a622/", "recommendations/11/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAS6wEYBvX0e-nHs8zlHMXiXG8osIMdXKaE", "recommendations/12/context": "Pascal was senior to Dean but didn't manage Dean directly", "recommendations/12/date": "April 25, 2010", "recommendations/12/description": "At the time at the Hyatt West Hollywood, Dean was probably the most energetic concierge/bellman you can think of.\nHe would go out of his way to help guests to ensure they got the information they were asking for. His communication was always in a pleasant and humoristic approach which was well appreciated by all.", "recommendations/12/name": "Dean Arevalo", "recommendations/12/subtitle": "Assistant Guest Experience Manager at Andaz West Hollywood", "recommendations/12/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/deanarevalo/", "recommendations/12/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAND7wYBjtw2PBjeYxJbd0pxmcc12asbI6U", "recommendations/13/context": "Pascal reported directly to Mark", "recommendations/13/date": "December 19, 2009", "recommendations/13/description": "While heading up the revenue and reservations Departments at the Hyatt West Hollywood, Mark was the Director of Operations.\n\nMark's hands on aproach made him a very effective manager. His eye for detail and ability to transfer his knowledge to the team were great motivators for everyone.\nMark is passionate and quality oriented and a great driver for change.", "recommendations/13/name": "Mark Van Cooney", "recommendations/13/subtitle": "General Manager Westin San Diego Bayview", "recommendations/13/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/mark-van-cooney-619a352/", "recommendations/13/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAACCMDUBecdlwCi1HInwPCOKbC1v3iWtRkg", "recommendations/14/context": "Pascal worked with Jennifer but on different teams", "recommendations/14/date": "November 14, 2009", "recommendations/14/description": "I attended the Executive Revenue Course facilitated by Jenn. Her methods of delivering the material made the course interesting every step of the way. With her cultural awareness, communication skills and knowledge sh is able to keep an entire class focussed for several days.\n\nJenn organized the extensive Revenue Acadamy in Cairo which was a great success with many participants. Her organizational skills and flexibility to adapt are a great asset.", "recommendations/14/name": "Jennifer Harris (Keen)", "recommendations/14/subtitle": "Training & Development Consultant | Change & Empowerment Programmes | Helping Leaders & Teams Thrive", "recommendations/14/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/jennifer-harris-keen-6445494/", "recommendations/14/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAADKwFQBl-y7luUKybA1a5mbNX43tEtTxTQ", "recommendations/15/context": "Pascal reported directly to Christine", "recommendations/15/date": "October 26, 2009", "recommendations/15/description": "Being the Revenue Manager and later the Executive Housekeeper at the Hyatt West Hollywood (Andaz), I reported directly to the Christine, Director of Operations.\nChristine's flexibility and innovative way of approaching challenges was a great motivator for me. \nDedication, profvessionalism and guest satisfation are key words displayed from Christine's organization and actions. Christine has a pleasant demeanour even when under extreme pressure which made working with her a pleasure.\nI would welcome the chance to work with Christine again in the future.", "recommendations/15/name": "Christine Aubele", "recommendations/15/subtitle": "Corporate Director of HR, US Operations at Westmont Hospitality Group", "recommendations/15/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/christineaubele/", "recommendations/15/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAJLXL8BP1xHGUEzgldy-c1ZfdyP0dZ0PCw", "recommendations/16/context": "Pascal was Gauthier's client", "recommendations/16/date": "October 4, 2009", "recommendations/16/description": "I have worked with Gauthier on several projects within our hotel and his dedication and precision makes the difference to achieve a great result.\n\nKnowledge and coordination are the key attributes in Gauthier's work.", "recommendations/16/name": "Gauthier Guillaume", "recommendations/16/subtitle": "Founder & CEO at GG&Grace International | Hospitality Design & Guest Experience Strategist | Concept Strategy, Storytelling & Execution", "recommendations/16/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/gauthguillaume/", "recommendations/16/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAABOW3QBamdCVNGrys9zYyfu2-cxqDl54KY", "recommendations/17/context": "Pascal worked with Louis on the same team", "recommendations/17/date": "September 4, 2009", "recommendations/17/description": "I have worked with Louis on several new upcoming projects in Cairo for IHG. Louis' in depth knowledge of how a hotel should be set up during the design stage is great. At the same time his eye for detail on some important issues is very important for long term operational success.\nHis passion and dedication to get things done correctly is admirable and will make him very succesful.", "recommendations/17/name": "Louis Mifsud", "recommendations/17/subtitle": "Proprietor at Dynamic Design Consultants Pty Ltd", "recommendations/17/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/louismifsud/", "recommendations/17/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAFVs6sBUR0Q5cmzgOPqSt4I8bEpKqinux0", "recommendations/18/context": "Pascal was senior to Michael but didn't manage Michael directly", "recommendations/18/date": "August 31, 2009", "recommendations/18/description": "Michael and I have worked together for more than 1.5 years and Michael is a dedicated and passionate F&B professional. \nHe has new ideas and implements new ways of presenting items. He is guarding quality and puts service and consistency on the top of his list.\n\nWith InterContinental he was able to manage all outlets with a large team. It shows from his experience that Michael has worked in quality operations.", "recommendations/18/name": "Michael Farquhar", "recommendations/18/subtitle": "COO @ ETM Group | Hospitality Expert Guiding Profitable Concepts", "recommendations/18/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/farquhar/", "recommendations/18/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAHGmKcB1efHcn8lepDy9Yo-Zg94bHDsswg", "recommendations/19/context": "Pascal worked with Christoph on the same team", "recommendations/19/date": "September 17, 2007", "recommendations/19/description": "I have worked together with Christoph at the Hyatt in Los Angeles and he has shown good knowledge of the F&B Operations and good understanding of overal managing all F&B outlets.\nHe doesn't mind working hard and insists on achieving the best results.", "recommendations/19/name": "Christoph Travniczek", "recommendations/19/subtitle": "General Manager at Flemings Selection Hotel Wien - City, managed by Motel One Austria GmbH", "recommendations/19/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/christoph-travniczek-56817b1/", "recommendations/19/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAAz4GABEA3JNIwc7_XUFbgpb3JjanydeMU", "recommendationsReceived/0/context": "Pascal was senior to Michaela but didn't manage Michaela directly", "recommendationsReceived/0/date": "September 28, 2019", "recommendationsReceived/0/description": "Pascal is a Leader who inspires by being on the ground with his people. Supporting, coaching and simply being a great human being. And teams want to supporting him back by delivering results. I am very thankful for having an opportunity to work in Pascal’s team. ", "recommendationsReceived/0/name": "Michaela Smith", "recommendationsReceived/0/subtitle": "Success & Imposter Syndrome Coach 👉 Enhance Your Nervous System For Success", "recommendationsReceived/0/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/smith-michaela/", "recommendationsReceived/0/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAdz0TIB_H0iZqOyd39Vd53ov5FedRFEb2I", "recommendationsReceived/1/context": "Craig worked with Pascal but they were at different companies", "recommendationsReceived/1/date": "September 27, 2019", "recommendationsReceived/1/description": "I've had the privilege of working with Pascal for the past 2 years, in his capacity as GM of InterCon Bandung.\n\nThroughout this time Pascal has been a motivating, decisive and results-orientated professional, with a strong focus on open and clear communication to articulate ideas and drive change and strategy,.\n\nThe commercial success his business has achieved during our tenure together bears testimony to his exceptional competencies as a luxury hotelier.", "recommendationsReceived/1/name": "Craig Winnett", "recommendationsReceived/1/subtitle": "CRM, Mobile Apps, Loyalty, Data, POS & Systems Integration", "recommendationsReceived/1/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/craig-winnett-10726a170/", "recommendationsReceived/1/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAACieAhcB7DlWVQT4Ndq4Sa9L0XNCTkV_gMA", "recommendationsReceived/2/context": "Jimmy worked with Pascal on the same team", "recommendationsReceived/2/date": "September 26, 2019", "recommendationsReceived/2/description": "I have been extremely fortunate to have worked with an inspirational leader in Pascal, I have worked directly and closely with Pascal managing InterContinental Nha Trang. Pascal takes a team approach to planning and plans from bottom up involving high levels of staff involvement and consultation. Pascal selects and builds good team players around him and emphasizes on staff development, he always encourages subordinates to solver their own problems thereby enhancing their on the job experience and instilling self-belief. Pascal is also very result oriented, his plans and strategies always have a vision to ensure achieving the goals which are most certainly realistic.\n\nHaving Pascal as the General Manager of InterContinental Nha Trang during my association with the property I have always seen him being very comfortable in his leadership role, I give my full recommendation. ", "recommendationsReceived/2/name": "Jimmy Jacob", "recommendationsReceived/2/subtitle": "Head of Media APAC & ME at Sabre Corporation", "recommendationsReceived/2/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/jimmy-jacob-69100617/", "recommendationsReceived/2/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAANh3E0B3HuOWG19zK-V_Ph-Mc8gSkojRy8", "recommendationsReceived/3/context": "Patric reported directly to Pascal", "recommendationsReceived/3/date": "October 27, 2018", "recommendationsReceived/3/description": "I had the privilege to work with Pascal at the Intercontinental Saigon during my time there. Pascal was my direct supervisor in the role of Hotel Manager. Pascal always supported me in all ways to be a successful. He leaves you space to mange your own task and keep you close in the crunch times where you can learn a lot from his great operational experience. \n\nPascal is a true hotelier, I learned a lot under his leadership, especially his coaching skills great, I still use his style as a model for me today.", "recommendationsReceived/3/name": "Patric Hadorn", "recommendationsReceived/3/subtitle": "General Manager, Operations at The Peninsula London", "recommendationsReceived/3/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/patrichadorn/", "recommendationsReceived/3/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAATSBmMByVw2Ex04X7l4oP9F1xCTYtQKe9I", "recommendationsReceived/4/context": "James managed Pascal directly", "recommendationsReceived/4/date": "September 28, 2018", "recommendationsReceived/4/description": "I worked with Pascal when he was Hotel Manager of the InterContinental Asiana Saigon and then when he took on his first General Manager role at the InterContinental Nha Trang. Pascal is an experienced, approachable hospitality leader who is able to handle the needs of many different stakeholders, be they guests, colleagues or hotel owners. He builds effective relationships and understands his business from A to Z, always focusing on what is required to deliver a great guest and employee experience. This is coupled with a strong commercial acumen.  All of these points ensure he delivers great results - on a consistent basis.", "recommendationsReceived/4/name": "James Young", "recommendationsReceived/4/subtitle": "Hospitality Operator & Leader 9 countries | Europe, Middle East, SE Asia & Australasia | IHG & WMC Group | Multi-unit operations & sustainable growth | Award-winning hotels & teams in Vietnam | MBA with Distinction | FIH", "recommendationsReceived/4/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/jamesyounglxvii/", "recommendationsReceived/4/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAABwc2IBp_PXsnfIWFt8iskhzmnNiQRuW5s", "recommendationsReceived/5/context": "Tara reported directly to Pascal", "recommendationsReceived/5/date": "September 25, 2018", "recommendationsReceived/5/description": "It’s rare to have the opportunity to report to a manager who is also a mentor. I had the utmost pleasure of working with Pascal at the Intercontinental Saigon. I am most impressed with Pascal’s ability to bring people together, even people who were initially on completely different viewpoints.  I would love to once again be part of his team.  ", "recommendationsReceived/5/name": "Tara Nguyen", "recommendationsReceived/5/subtitle": "20yr Global Hotel People Leader - IHG, Four Seasons, and Rosewood - Leadership roles in both US and Asia", "recommendationsReceived/5/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/taranguyen/", "recommendationsReceived/5/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAABHvAv0BJeNZmhvTYfnD1YQUGGcW6UprEXk", "recommendationsReceived/6/context": "Michel worked with Pascal on the same team", "recommendationsReceived/6/date": "September 24, 2018", "recommendationsReceived/6/description": "“Pascal is a great Hospitality leader whom has the ability to connect with his team, customers and stakeholders to achieve outstanding performance “", "recommendationsReceived/6/name": "Michel Chertouh", "recommendationsReceived/6/subtitle": "Luxury Hospitality Leader | Managing Director at Regent Hong Kong", "recommendationsReceived/6/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/michel-chertouh-901408/", "recommendationsReceived/6/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAAPaxEBeTzLsemqRqlP39NS20t3LOw1TdM", "recommendationsReceived/7/context": "Adam worked with Pascal on the same team", "recommendationsReceived/7/date": "September 21, 2018", "recommendationsReceived/7/description": "Outstanding hotelier, focused on people both Guest and colleague always with a view on driving financial results\n.\n", "recommendationsReceived/7/name": "Adam McDonald", "recommendationsReceived/7/subtitle": "General Manager -Owner Advocacy -Opening Specialist -Brand Ambassador -Project Management -Luxury Operator -Coaching and Mentoring -Hotel Management - Asset Management", "recommendationsReceived/7/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/adammcdonaldgeneralmanager/", "recommendationsReceived/7/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAhzH7QBClDE3tf3WuSarukJ7pXnbHAN3Cc", "recommendationsReceived/8/context": "Andrew was Pascal's client", "recommendationsReceived/8/date": "December 24, 2016", "recommendationsReceived/8/description": "I have no hesitation in recommending Pascal, I stayed numerous times when he was the manager at the Intercontinental in Nha Trang Vietnam, the service he gave was second to none, the staff he managed gave excellent service and made us felt most welcome which was why we stayed many times.\nI look forward to staying at his new hotel in Bandung.", "recommendationsReceived/8/name": "Andrew Goddard", "recommendationsReceived/8/subtitle": "CEO", "recommendationsReceived/8/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/andrew-goddard-3474063b/", "recommendationsReceived/8/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAhsymcB8PUyxBcXU5vI3EymL9wJLrNov1Q", "recommendationsReceived/9/context": "Omar worked with Pascal on the same team", "recommendationsReceived/9/date": "December 1, 2014", "recommendationsReceived/9/description": "I have worked with Pascal for almost 6 years at Citystars in Cairo, during this period Pascal showed a great example of how a leader should be, he was always connected to all colleagues on all levels, he has always delivered great results and was very well known for his attention to details and follow up. for these reasons Pascal was appointed to be in-charge of the greatest and the biggest event for IHG Citystars at that time in 2010, it was the IHG Owners' and GMs' conference. He collected a team from the three hotels and created a work group that i was part of and it was the experience of my life to learn from Pascal how giant projects can easily be implemented and how to get the buy in from all team members towards a common goal. Pascal was one of the few who affected my career life, i learned from him two things, the first is that follow up on my work is the key to success, and the second is getting closer to the staff and being one of them, this will add up to my emotional bank account credit and will allow me to achieve more through my people.  ", "recommendationsReceived/9/name": "Omar Wasfy", "recommendationsReceived/9/subtitle": "Area Director of Human Resources - UAE, PES", "recommendationsReceived/9/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/omar-wasfy-6310201a/", "recommendationsReceived/9/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAPrBYUB6varmTTG4dTNfYphbYZmIQF5l1g", "recommendationsReceived/10/context": "Antonio reported directly to Pascal", "recommendationsReceived/10/date": "October 24, 2012", "recommendationsReceived/10/description": "I worked with Pascal for almost 2 years in InterContinental Asiana Saigon. he is a very passionate Hotel Manager who puts people first in his way of managing the hotel operations.He has shown tremendous improvements in terms of people engagement to their jobs. Pascal is business savvy Manager who drives business with the highest efficiency and achieving targets by applying common business sense. Most importantly, Pascal's support to achieving great results in Managing Risk and running a safe hotel has helped the team achieved desired targets, Thanks for his dedication and consistent follow through. With Pascal on board, our Hotel changed from Good to Great! He maintains a work life balance by properly managing his time, which is just the right thing to do. I wish all the best to Pascal in all his future endeavors.", "recommendationsReceived/10/name": "Antonio Dizon, PME,CEOE,CEM", "recommendationsReceived/10/subtitle": "Director Of Engineering at Shangri-La The Fort Manila", "recommendationsReceived/10/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/antonio-dizon-pme-ceoe-cem-5b50258/", "recommendationsReceived/10/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAFtRxkBTs5zFmZiY9PLCKDky4Li3WLS9d0", "recommendationsReceived/11/context": "Bill worked with Pascal on the same team", "recommendationsReceived/11/date": "May 13, 2011", "recommendationsReceived/11/description": "Pascal is an excellent manager who balances well the needs of the guest, staff, suppliers and principals.  He listens well and quickly constructs ideas and solutions to meet the stakeholders needs.  In addition, he's a great guy who likes to have fun when working.", "recommendationsReceived/11/name": "Bill Burton", "recommendationsReceived/11/subtitle": "Meetings and Events Consultant", "recommendationsReceived/11/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/bill-burton-34773a1/", "recommendationsReceived/11/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAABJXGcBkKDGkudMgfZ3MD2dpjBtFIDbrVk", "recommendationsReceived/12/context": "Ken worked with Pascal on the same team", "recommendationsReceived/12/date": "December 10, 2010", "recommendationsReceived/12/description": "Pascal's passion for the business and attention for detail and leadership at the InterContinental Cairo Citystars hotel was evident at our event that we held in November 2010.  From the minute we began our planning sessions to the final execution of the event, Pascal made creative suggestions, rallied his team behind our event and personally made himself present at all the pressure points.  Aside from his command of the operations, Pascal also had a great sense of humour that strong relationships around the complex to help make things happen.  We had possibly the best conference ever in my my lifetime", "recommendationsReceived/12/name": "Ken Pahkim", "recommendationsReceived/12/subtitle": "Event Producer and Strategic Events Manager. Service design experience, event and production management", "recommendationsReceived/12/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/kenpahkim/", "recommendationsReceived/12/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAABGlAEBZ7Yx63Qs9uk1SYzHvhcJQdlv_aI", "recommendationsReceived/13/context": "Stephen was Pascal's client", "recommendationsReceived/13/date": "December 6, 2010", "recommendationsReceived/13/description": "I have just finished an extensive project for the most demanding client in the World - the conference at City Stars was a huge success and was led Hotel side by Pascal and his team of over 1100. The Client has rated it as their best ever conference – in a tough and difficult market Pascal has the rare ability to get the most out of all his team and to do it quietly, effectively and with a lot of charm and style. A born leader who inspires great things in other people.  I look forward to working with him again.\n\nStephen Knight Managing Director Pimento", "recommendationsReceived/13/name": "Stephen Knight", "recommendationsReceived/13/subtitle": "Founder, Pimento | Connecting brands with the UK’s best independent marketing agencies. Chairman of utc.travel the UKs leading travel membership club that offers travel at trade prices.", "recommendationsReceived/13/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/stephen-knight-uk/", "recommendationsReceived/13/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAF1NWEBgGkZy4KuPlVfrdKOlkgZkUPPcMk", "recommendationsReceived/14/context": "Michael worked with Pascal on the same team", "recommendationsReceived/14/date": "September 24, 2010", "recommendationsReceived/14/description": "Pascal was a joy to work with and I worked for him for over 2 years. He is a take-charge person who is able to present creative ideas and communicate the benefits. His attention to detail and focus on results makes him a key asset to any organization. It was a real pleasure to work with Pascal.", "recommendationsReceived/14/name": "Michael Farquhar", "recommendationsReceived/14/subtitle": "COO @ ETM Group | Hospitality Expert Guiding Profitable Concepts", "recommendationsReceived/14/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/farquhar/", "recommendationsReceived/14/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAHGmKcB1efHcn8lepDy9Yo-Zg94bHDsswg", "recommendationsReceived/15/context": "Mark managed Pascal directly", "recommendationsReceived/15/date": "December 18, 2009", "recommendationsReceived/15/description": "Pascal was Director of Revenue Management at the Hyatt West Hollywood.  Pascal's understanding of revenue management, monitoring rates, and developing promotions that worked in a busy market was impressive.  Pascal was able to lead our revenue management team, come prepared with his recommendations and effectively manage and yield our inventory to produce impressive results in terms of STAR performance and market share.\n\nPascal is detail oriented, passionate and consistently looks for ways to improve hotel operations and results.\n\nI would highly recommend Pascal and would love to work with him again in the future.", "recommendationsReceived/15/name": "Mark Van Cooney", "recommendationsReceived/15/subtitle": "General Manager Westin San Diego Bayview", "recommendationsReceived/15/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/mark-van-cooney-619a352/", "recommendationsReceived/15/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAACCMDUBecdlwCi1HInwPCOKbC1v3iWtRkg", "recommendationsReceived/16/context": "Jennifer worked with Pascal but on different teams", "recommendationsReceived/16/date": "September 15, 2009", "recommendationsReceived/16/description": "Pascal is, without doubt, a passionate hotelier who strives for perfection in all that he undertakes.  As an operator, I was always impressed with Pascal’s in-depth knowledge of so many different areas of the business - and yet he is always keen to learn more and continue to develop.  Pascal is objective and reasoned, but still retains sight of people (both colleagues and guests) in his decision making process.  A quick wit and sharp brain - Pascal will keep you on your toes!", "recommendationsReceived/16/name": "Jennifer Harris (Keen)", "recommendationsReceived/16/subtitle": "Training & Development Consultant | Change & Empowerment Programmes | Helping Leaders & Teams Thrive", "recommendationsReceived/16/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/jennifer-harris-keen-6445494/", "recommendationsReceived/16/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAADKwFQBl-y7luUKybA1a5mbNX43tEtTxTQ", "recommendationsReceived/17/context": "Louis worked with Pascal on the same team", "recommendationsReceived/17/date": "September 8, 2009", "recommendationsReceived/17/description": "“In my role as Director of Design I was responsible for all new hotel designs, refurbishments and expansion projects in Egypt for a period of about 12 months. I met Pascal from the start of this tenure. Pascal was involved in giving operational support to me for renovation, design and construction projects at InterContinental City Stars Hotel in Cairo. His approach and support was always timely, very professional and diligent. This assisted me in giving our owners the correct advice not only from the Design side but also the operational requirements and aspects of the business. Pascal has a pleasant demeanour even when under extreme pressure which made working with him a pleasure. I look forward to working with Pascal again in the future.”", "recommendationsReceived/17/name": "Louis Mifsud", "recommendationsReceived/17/subtitle": "Proprietor at Dynamic Design Consultants Pty Ltd", "recommendationsReceived/17/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/louismifsud/", "recommendationsReceived/17/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAFVs6sBUR0Q5cmzgOPqSt4I8bEpKqinux0", "recommendationsReceived/18/context": "Remko worked with Pascal on the same team", "recommendationsReceived/18/date": "September 5, 2009", "recommendationsReceived/18/description": "Integrity, passion and vision are terms that come to mind when working with Pascal. Combined with a sense of humor it makes for the perfect mix of characteristics for a hospitality leader. It is my expectation that Pascal will always 'happen' to end up on the winning team. \n\nRemko Engelman\nDirector of Operations Hard Rock Cafe", "recommendationsReceived/18/name": "Remko Engelman", "recommendationsReceived/18/subtitle": "Hotel Manager Mitland Hotel", "recommendationsReceived/18/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/remkoengelman/", "recommendationsReceived/18/urn": "