n Hotel Wien - City, managed by Motel One Austria GmbH", "recommendationsReceived/20/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/christoph-travniczek-56817b1/", "recommendationsReceived/20/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAAz4GABEA3JNIwc7_XUFbgpb3JjanydeMU", "recommendationsReceived/21/context": "Bokke worked with Pascal but they were at different companies", "recommendationsReceived/21/date": "March 9, 2007", "recommendationsReceived/21/description": "In the time we were both located in Shanghai in the early 90's during  the first great influx of western business delegations, I was in regular contact with Pascal in my capacity of organizor of such delegations, business dinners and seminars which took place in the Worldfield Convention hotel in which Pascal was working at the time. Pascal's attention to detail, his creativity, his knowlegde of the hospitality business and his excellent communication skills all contributed to the 100% success rate we had on the events organized. I can therefore highly recomment the services of Pascal.", "recommendationsReceived/21/name": "Bokke Veltkamp", "recommendationsReceived/21/subtitle": "Int'l Business Development at C. Steinweg Handelsveem B.V.", "recommendationsReceived/21/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/bokke/", "recommendationsReceived/21/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAACEOS8BIl1zz52KjFKC93t_dXqqOz_M5_U", "skills/0/title": "Executive Management", "skills/1/title": "Rooms Division", "skills/2/title": "Hotel Management", "skills/3/title": "Customer Satisfaction", "skills/4/title": "Guest Satisfaction", "skills/5/title": "Employee Relations", "skills/6/title": "cost control", "skills/7/title": "Revenue Management", "skills/8/title": "Team Leadership", "skills/9/title": "Event Management", "skills/10/title": "Operations Management", "skills/11/title": "Food & Beverage", "skills/12/title": "Budget Management", "skills/13/title": "Forecasting", "skills/14/title": "championing change", "skills/15/title": "Strategic Thinking", "skills/16/