y Macau.  There were a number of facility challenges and plenty of projects with the hotel at the time, which CW planned well to address and showed great resolve and problem solving skills.  Always positive and searching for solutions, not one to give in easily, a true professional.", "recommendations/1/name": "C.W. Chiu", "recommendations/1/subtitle": "Assistant Director at Wynn Palace", "recommendations/1/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/c-w-chiu-515b1928/", "recommendations/1/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAXcVKEBbqWEdvxMmWwSTTafk4rEKwPuCAI", "recommendations/2/context": "Joseph managed Anung directly", "recommendations/2/date": "August 24, 2012", "recommendations/2/description": "Anung was a real pleasure to have as an Assistant F&B Manager, with a great work ethic, able to rally the team, extremly creative, and excellent customer service attention.  Anung helped me immensly to drive the service standards and implement Destination Dining concepts while at Banyan Tree Bintan.  As leaders, we cannot achieve anything without a solid team, and that was achieved through Anung's energy and creative spirit.  A great addition to any team.", "recommendations/2/name": "Anung Prihastomo", "recommendations/2/subtitle": "Operations Manager at Natra Bintan, Tribute Portfolio", "recommendations/2/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/anung-prihastomo-53875b14/", "recommendations/2/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAL1djwBPwVnpR8iDs3PHDnIMly9PzznVJM", "recommendations/3/context": "Joseph worked with Richard on the same team", "recommendations/3/date": "September 28, 2010", "recommendations/3/description": "Richard is the all round Food and Beverage Guru from conceptualization to operation.  Very knowledgeable on all aspects down to technical specs and great advise.  Had the pleasure of dealing with Richard on a couple of projects with Sunswepts and found him a great personality and professional to the detail.", "recommendations/3/name": "Richard Lovett", "recommendations/3/subtitle": "Looking for a new challenge", "recommendations/3/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/richard-lovett-86b3975/", "recommendations/3/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAADyQRMBtfDtEIMM1kKKi7bq5yybwP2OkQA", "recommendations/4/context": "Joseph worked with Kevin B. on the same team", "recommendations/4/date": "September 27, 2010", "recommendations/4/description": "Kevin has fantastic energy and great attention to detail.  Passionate about food and produce and will not accept second best.  Inspirational leader and able to get the best out of all team members, gained a lot of respect in a challenging environment.  As an F&B at the time, it was a pleasure to work with someone of Kevin’s caliber.", "recommendations/4/name": "Kevin B. Thomson", "recommendations/4/subtitle": "Executive Chef - JW Marriott Bangkok, Thailand", "recommendations/4/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/kevin-b-thomson-54809810/", "recommendations/4/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAIl0ggB0HUVk7Hgm4RdH4C6GdXiTkRNMP4", "recommendationsReceived/0/context": "François managed Joseph directly", "recommendationsReceived/0/date": "September 26, 2012", "recommendationsReceived/0/description": "Joseph and I worked together in Bintan. I was looking for someone to work closely with the team and adapt to the local culture so the management team would have a strong positive leadership on the Laguna Bintan Resorts Complex. Joseph came in and just did that with his friendly approachable attitude and won over the Indonesian team rapidly, Together we created the Dining Destination which at the time supported the repositioning of the destination and became the biggest revenue and PR generator in F&B and for the resort. While achieving great services offer Joseph never lost managing the financial aspect of the F&B department and achieved fantastic results, creating specific menu engineering program and managing very efficiently.  \n  \nSince Joseph has carried on successfully his career path within BanyanTree Hotels & Resorts doing opening in China and Macau and becoming an excellent hotelier. His technical and human skills, International experience, opening experience, resort, city and casino hotel experience can only sets him for a fantastic career in the hospitality industry. \n\nI cannot wait to see what we will be his next assignment.", "recommendationsReceived/0/name": "François Huet", "recommendationsReceived/0/subtitle": "🎙️ Auteur du podcast Xperientiel | 🌱 Producteur de podcasts engagés | 🤝 Facilitateur de transitions écologiques et humaines", "recommendationsReceived/0/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/françois-huet-a6527a14/", "recommendationsReceived/0/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAALjGG0BW1l_2Bc0PwwZiXw9Ev1rD3aBFl8", "recommendationsReceived/1/context": "Andrew worked with Joseph on the same team", "recommendationsReceived/1/date": "February 18, 2011", "recommendationsReceived/1/description": "While Joseph and I worked together I was impressed by his ability to lead his team from the front. He laid out simple and clear goals to which he held his team to account. His craft skills were such that he was able to help the staff members doing their jobs and with Supervisors he gave them the tools to be more effective. I would be happy to have him join our team again.", "recommendationsReceived/1/name": "Andrew Barnard", "recommendationsReceived/1/subtitle": "CEO at SunSwept Resorts - YPO chapter - Southern Caribbean Integrated & Lisbon", "recommendationsReceived/1/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/thebodyholidaygm/", "recommendationsReceived/1/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAABR5LMBdNEUQzyU4-LL71CnA5bnoHyE2cY", "skills/0/title": "Employee Relations", "skills/1/title": "Leadership", "skills/2/title": "Financial Literacy", "skills/3/title": "Customer Service", "skills/4/title": "Destination Dining", "skills/5/title": "Resort Operations", "skills/6/title": "Integrated Resort", "skills/7/title": "F&B Concept Development", "skills/8/title": "Cash Flow", "skills/9/title": "P&L Management", "skills/10/title": "Operations Management", "skills/11/title": "Budgeting", "skills/12/title": "Sales & Marketing", "skills/13/title": "Project Management", "skills/14/title": "Pre-opening", "skills/15/title": "Resorts", "skills/16/title": "Hotel Management", "skills/17/title": "Food & Beverage", "skills/18/title": "Hospitality Industry", "skills/19/title": "Restaurants", "totalExperienceYears": "30.8", "totalRecommendationsGiven": "5", "totalRecommendationsReceived": "2", "urn": "ACoAAAFbuncB_R60QwpJKjpmli8F7IDmQcyUzX4"}$$::jsonb),
